<view class="page">
  <view class="status-panel">
    <view class="status-title">{{statusTitle}}</view>
    <view class="status-detail">{{statusDetail}}</view>
    <view wx:if="{{feedback}}" class="feedback">{{feedback}}</view>
  </view>

  <view class="score-panel">
    <view class="score-item">
      <text class="score-label">X</text>
      <text class="score-value">{{scores.X}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="score-item">
      <text class="score-label">O</text>
      <text class="score-value">{{scores.O}}</text>
    </view>
    <view class="score-item">
      <text class="score-label">平局</text>
      <text class="score-value">{{scores.draw}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="control-panel">
    <view class="control-label">游戏模式</view>
    <view class="segmented">
      <button
        wx:for="{{modeOptions}}"
        wx:key="value"
        class="segment-button {{gameMode === item.value ? 'is-active' : ''}}"
        data-mode="{{item.value}}"
        bindtap="handleModeTap"
      >
        {{item.label}}
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{gameMode === 'computer'}}" class="control-panel">
    <view class="control-label">AI 难度</view>
    <view class="segmented difficulty">
      <button
        wx:for="{{difficultyOptions}}"
        wx:key="value"
        class="segment-button {{aiDifficulty === item.value ? 'is-active' : ''}}"
        data-difficulty="{{item.value}}"
        bindtap="handleDifficultyTap"
      >
        {{item.label}}
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="board-wrap">
    <view class="macro-board">
      <view
        wx:for="{{boards}}"
        wx:for-item="board"
        wx:key="boardIndex"
        class="{{board.classes}}"
      >
        <view class="board-meta">
          <text>{{board.name}}</text>
          <text wx:if="{{board.winner}}" class="owner-badge">{{board.winner}}</text>
          <text wx:elif="{{board.full}}" class="full-badge">满</text>
        </view>
        <view class="cell-grid">
          <view
            wx:for="{{board.cells}}"
            wx:for-item="cell"
            wx:key="cellIndex"
            class="{{cell.classes}}"
            data-board-index="{{board.boardIndex}}"
            data-cell-index="{{cell.cellIndex}}"
            bindtap="handleCellTap"
          >
            {{cell.value}}
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="actions">
    <button class="action-button" bindtap="handleUndo" disabled="{{moveHistory.length === 0 || isComputerThinking}}">
      撤销
    </button>
    <button class="action-button" bindtap="handleRestart">
      重新开始
    </button>
    <button class="action-button" bindtap="handleResetScores">
      重置比分
    </button>
    <button class="action-button" bindtap="showRules">
      规则
    </button>
  </view>

  <view class="history-panel">
    <view class="history-header">
      <text class="section-title">落子历史</text>
      <button
        wx:if="{{moveHistory.length > 6}}"
        class="link-button"
        bindtap="toggleHistory"
      >
        {{historyExpanded ? '收起' : '展开'}}
      </button>
    </view>
    <view wx:if="{{displayedHistory.length === 0}}" class="empty-history">还没有落子</view>
    <view wx:else class="history-list">
      <view wx:for="{{displayedHistory}}" wx:key="step" class="history-item">
        {{item.text}}
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{rulesVisible}}" class="modal-mask" catchtap="hideRules">
    <view class="rules-dialog" catchtap="noop">
      <view class="rules-title">游戏规则</view>
      <view class="rules-text">
        <view>棋盘由 9 个小棋盘组成。你下在哪个小格，对手下一步就要去对应位置的小棋盘。</view>
        <view>如果目标小棋盘已满，对手可以自由选择其他未满小棋盘。</view>
        <view>小棋盘三连后会归属给获胜玩家，但只要还有空格，仍然可以继续落子。</view>
        <view>已归属小棋盘的归属不会改变，后续落子仍会控制对手下一步的位置。</view>
        <view>大棋盘上先占领三个连成一线的小棋盘即可获胜。</view>
      </view>
      <button class="primary-button" bindtap="hideRules">知道了</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
